An inquiry was forwarded to me regarding oversight of homeowners' associations.  

The Department of the Secretary of State does handle incorporations of nonprofit corporations and unincorporated associations.  Many homeowners' associations are incorporated as nonprofits.  The Department does not, however, regulate homeowners' associations.  Internal management issues in homeowners' associations are a matter for the members of the associations to resolve, either through their internal by-laws processes or by using the courts system.

